title: CSV to WordPress Import Plugin v1.6
description:
CSV to WordPress Import plugin is a very useful tool for anybody who wants to bulk import data from CSV file to Wordpress. Plugin works on all recent AitThemes starting from Creator theme upwards, ending with Business Finder theme. You can import data to any Wordpress Custom Type we have. For example plugin can be used to bulk import Directory Theme items, Ristorante Theme menus, Testimonials and so on. Plugin can be also used to upload posts and pages.

Product page: http://codecanyon.net/item/csv-to-wordpress-import-plugin/4829224

This plugin has been fully nulled, to install simply upload it to your host like you would any other wordpress plugin.
